{"type": "article", "id": 25997, "title": "小胖不再是Lanvin董事会成员，以及，VOGUE神话大片令人惊叹｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-26T10:54:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16044, "name": "大片"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 6579, "name": "春夏系列"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 26754, "name": "高定系列"}, {"id": 26755, "name": "董事会"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 10714, "name": "万宝龙"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702121806mMa5oYA2jvbVtLH6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Christoph-Auhagen-departs-Hugo-Boss,686059.html#rc\"><b>Hugo Boss CBO 离职</b></a>｜德国奢侈品牌 Hugo Boss 宣布其首席商务官（Chief Business Officer）Christoph Auhagen 离职，后者作为 CBO 负责品牌、创意管理、采购及生产等已有六年。在此之前，Auhagen 在 Espirit 担任高级副总裁、在 Gerry Weber 担任经理。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Chanel-opens-jewelry-boutique-at-Bergdorf-Goodman,685587.html#rc\"><b>Chanel 在 Bergdorf Goodman 百货内开珠宝店</b></a>｜Chanel 近日宣布将在 Bergdorf Goodman 百货商店内开一家珠宝精品店，这是 Chanel 首次在多品牌零售商内开店。134 平方英尺的面积，展示 Chanel 的高级珠宝，价格在 1500-50000 美元之间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/alber-elbaz-dismissed-board-directors-lanvin-10417864/\"><b>Alber Elbaz 不再是 Lanvin 董事会成员</b></a>｜Lanvin 最近的董事会议决定，前创意总监 Alber Elbaz 离开董事会，Lanvin 已找到 Alber 的继任者，Bouchra Jarrar  将从2017 春季开始担任女装艺术总监。结束 14 年的任期后，此次退出，标志着 Alber 彻底停止与这家自己一手塑造的公司的关联、影响。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Interparfums-1st-quarter-revenue-driven-by-Montblanc,685435.html#.Vx7Cj4QrJQY\"><b>Montblanc 香水带动 Interparfums 一季度收益上涨</b></a>｜专注于制造及分销香水的法国集团 Interparfums，近日宣布一季度与去年同期相比上了 8.5%，有赖于 Montblanc 品牌销售额的驱动。1 月至 3 月，集团获得了 8370 万欧元的收益，其中仅 Montblanc 的销售额就占了 3180 万欧元。Montblanc 的收益上涨了 32%。Jimmy Choo 香水则上涨了 1% 至 1950 万欧元。另一方面，Lanvin 的香水由于在俄罗斯和中国市场遇冷，销售额下跌了 24%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/business/bottega-veneta-parco-palladiano-fragrances-10416905/\"><b>BV 推出 Palladian 公园系列香水</b></a>｜Bottega Veneta 最新推出的香水系列以意大利名胜古迹 “Parco Palladiano （意为 Palladian 公园）” 为灵感，原料包括在意大利的 Vicenza 区生长的有机草本、植物、花朵和水果，想要营造漫步公园般的香气。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/topshop-x-net-a-porter/\">Topshop 推出为奢侈品电商 Net-a-Porter 特别合作系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121752zX6vKYdNBHF2Px47.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021217537Fwx9K8cn3mT0pvz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121753VpNlQhDRejyXs7J6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/supreme-x-nike-air-max-98-official\">Supreme x Nike Air Max 98 推出 2016 年春季系列</a>，4 月 28 日线上开售，29 日登陆日本：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121754cNmBoF2Y89dkHs3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121754DtFMkUNsSnXLwK6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121755lXEHPySLWpobDnjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121755lQmwtafOj4Kh92NB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121756h8BalQFzArm16vC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121756BNA4jXrvw6MysKDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121757W81nMOlDUfX6zYqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">著名摄影师 Mariano Vivanco 为俄罗斯版本的<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/mariano-vivanco-haute-couture-vogue-russia/\"> <i>Vogue </i>五月刊拍摄了一组神话故事般的大片</a>，主要展示奢侈品牌们的春季高定系列，包括 Valentino 和 Chanel 等。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121757Yy53i7dB6XquUvhb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121758m91s24KwcYg8LzWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121758agYVterEwz4hdjfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121759Fcds2A5l9D1LtBrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121759Wsdgu6Tw0YPOm5Hx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121800tAGoqr89uZ6Mfjhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121800PCx9gvmKy6zADpIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Adidas 推出两款奢侈版本的 EQT 球鞋<a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/focus/athletic-outdoor/adidas-eqt-oddity-luxe-pack-sneakers-release-215154/\"> EQT Oddity Luxe 系列</a>，由鸵鸟皮、蛇皮、鳄鱼皮等制成，男女款价格分别在 120-160 美元之间，预计 5 月 6 日上市：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121801sPHE6x9Qt7cTwWRI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121801IVTyDYqrCWMkel1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121802HdbY5n74OuZgI9iN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/guess-spring-2016-campaign/\">Guess 2016 春夏系列</a>在米克诺斯岛（Mykonos）拍摄了特辑，延续品牌一贯的性感风格：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121802achmCSlXtGOz0KeJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121803x2IMoLPFuYO0c4Ns.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121803JPeg6LVzlfD1puXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121804FfCxZND8AKXqv9Bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121804FKlV57rxCG3IUozg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121805duS4FQtpHE38Z5OP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121805EXOxaeGIsrQ2Z7pH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121806qmBGMfA4rtoFjKcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}